agu, Alina |date=6 March 2020 |website=HotNews.ro |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200307161732/https://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-sanatate-23704639-8-lea-caz-infectie-coronavirus-confirmat-romania-femeie-51-ani-din-olt-care-intors-din-italia.htm |archive-date=7 March 2020 |access-date=6 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! 9\n| {{Success|Recovered}}<ref name=\"recovered-14-mar\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.ms.ro/2020/03/14/proceduri-de-externare-pentru-3-pacienti-internati-la-spitalul-de-boli-infectioase-timisoara |title=Proceduri de externare pentru 3 pacien\u021bi interna\u021bi la Spitalul de Boli Infec\u021bioase Timi\u0219oara |date=14 March 2020 |website=Ministerul S\u0103n\u0103t\u0103\u021bii |language=ro |access-date=14 March 2020}}</ref>\n| Imported case\n| {{flag|Italy}}\n| [[Hunedoara County|Hunedoara]]\n| Male\n| 44\n| \n| <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/al-optulea-caz-de-coronavirus-confirmat-in-romania-1271262 |title=Alte dou\u0103 cazuri de coronavirus confirmate vineri, \u00een Rom\u00e2nia. Noul bilan\u021b: 9 pacien\u021bi infecta\u021bi cu COVID-19 |date=6 March 2020 |website=Digi24}}</ref>\n|-\n! 10\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 7 Mar.\n| {{Success|Recovered}}<ref name=\"tion\" /><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.news.ro/social/doi-pacienti-internati-cu-coronavirus-in-timisoara-s-au-vindecat-si-vor-fi-externati-1922401210172020032019298449 |title=Doi pacien\u021bi interna\u021bi cu coronavirus \u00een Timi\u0219oara s-au vindecat \u0219i vor fi externa\u021bi |last=Iedu, Liliana |date=10 March 2020 |website=News.ro}}</ref>\n| Local transmission\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Timi\u0219 County|Timi\u0219]]\n| Female\n| 15\n| She is studying at the same high school with cases #5 and #7, but not in the same class.\n| <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-esential-23706416-alte-doua-cazuri-coronavirus-confirmate-romania-bilantul-ajunge-11.htm |title=Alte dou\u0103 cazuri de coronavirus confirmate \u00een Rom\u00e2nia. Bilan\u